      • whichDeclares

        public static SourceFile whichDeclares(io.spine.code.java.ClassName javaClass)
        Resolves the file which contains the declaration of the given class.

        The resulting SourceFile represents a relative path to the Java file starting at the top level package.

        In the simplest case, the file name is the same as the simple class name. However, if the class is nested, then the file name coincides with the simple name of the top-level class.

        Parameters:
        javaClass - the name of the class to resolve
        Returns:
        the file in which the Java class is declared
